=r%2B%2FiB006GaAC7ImnPZ1QyQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=dbc3e2fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://media.giphy.com/media/zwLrs16kHu7Ys/giphy.gifimg]</a></blockquote><br />\nChing 個簽名咁型"},{"pid":"d47e8d9cde2871495617733e2b10af6b93499dbb","tid":454170,"uid":14952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">意識</span>防守呀，冇聽過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14109d0dd0114d4b9508984635f978660c30bc85","tid":454170,"uid":123243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee47ace8293febf0b74e9430246642cadf74918","tid":454170,"uid":55193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理性討論, 依球係咪雷C唔應該追落去<br />\n前面果個繼續閘, 後面果個繼續包,  中間雷斯走開捉其他人?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係佢封左位都叫有用?</blockquote><br />\n雷斯同魯迪加都有問題 封位有azp其實都ok 雷斯應該跟後上既人 魯迪加身後追得就應該正正經經等迪清高轉身封佢位 而家衝埋入去變左3條友同一作用=冇作用"},{"pid":"d28fd265aea7cf5dbcd23b976f44484f3fa26623","tid":454170,"uid":114421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理性討論, 依球係咪雷C唔應該追落去<br />\n前面果個繼續閘, 後面果個繼續包,  中間雷斯走開捉其他人?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係佢封左位都叫有用?</blockquote><br />\n利: 無睇場波<br />\n最理想魯迪加放 去守遠柱後上 <br />\n雷斯上去逼 azp包 又或者可以係azp同雷斯一齊包<br />\n<br />\n理論上黎講魯迪加已經比人放開 兩個入面雷斯比較快佢去逼其實都正路<br />\n但明顯3個中堅好似踢街場咁 完全唔理隊友<br />\n<br />\nazp個企位應該睇到哂有人後上緊 佢無指揮魯迪加去補位/自己唔去補位 係佢問題<br />\n魯迪加比人爆過左追唔到都照追 唔去補位 係佢問題<br />\n雷斯唔信任azp 為左幫魯迪加個位而失位 係佢問題<br />\n古圖斯 身為龍門睇撚哂個大局大把時間見住人後上都唔指揮後防 佢好撚有問題"},{"pid":"0e3008fe7099d66529fe1309c69ea228f53cad91","tid":454170,"uid":137694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>理性討論, 依球係咪雷C唔應該追落去<br />\n前面果個繼續閘, 後面果個繼續包,  中間雷斯走開捉其他人?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定係佢封左位都叫有用?</blockquote><br />\n又唔係美CC朗,使撚3個一齊去,<br />\n最多兩個夾,一個守後上就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nC朗既話搵一個mark都夠啦<br />\n條tap in王一對一過人都成日自己仆街</blockquote><br />\nC朗係俾人圍易甩啫，一對一好勁喎"},{"pid":"c17a068d255ef6c6054b4b1365f25fa9e274a296","tid":454170,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"AZP都上埋腦<br />\n兩個人mark乜都夠啦"},{"pid":"509405113ca622bc0270d764f906f8b859a383dc","tid":454170,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f01a409709bf4d3a8d725f2798fded6ab4314f5","tid":454170,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"中間仲有艾沙拉維入緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af95484b6d143ba998667f65563dbe5dcde2959f","tid":454170,"uid":129862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"